messages.content: Hi! How can I help you today?

Hey there! I'm Noah Patel. Honestly, I'm a bit of a mess right now—this whole work-from-home situation has me feeling super anxious. 

I recently placed an order for some home office gear and hiking stuff because I was planning to head back to my parents' place in Seattle to work remotely and hit the trails. But of course, my company just announced we're heading back to the office soon! 

Is there any way I can cancel just the office items from my order but keep the hiking gear? I can't quite remember which specific office things I picked, though.
